Reach out to us at marketing@destinationbryan.com . Do you have a question about First Friday ? Send us an email at firstfriday@destinationbryan.com. For specific staff members' email addresses, visit our About Us page . Mailing & Physical Address Our office is located at Lake Walk near POV Coffee and Kanji Sushi. We're typically in the office Monday-Friday, 8:30-5:00, but we're a small staff and often running around town for events, meetings, etc. Please call ahead before stopping by the office to make sure someone will be there to welcome you. Address: 3989 N Shore Dr Bryan, Texas 77807 Phone We can be reached by phone at the number below, however – given the nature of what we do and how frequently we are out of the office meeting with various partners, supporting local events, etc. – email is often the best way to reach us. (979) 721-9506 About Us Destination Bryan is the official destination marketing organization for Bryan, Texas.
